title: Club Naked
description:
Tachibana is an unsatisfied system engineer without a girlfriend.
One day, he was forcibly taken by a female boss at CLUB NAKED, a strip club where a man takes off his clothes. Among them, the number one dancer Leo caught his eye.
Tachibana falls in love with Leo's powerful dance, outfits that stimulate sympathy, and his beautiful physical body!!

“I never thought I'd be mesmerized by a man's naked body.
When I came to my senses, I was taken aback that I went there every week?!”
